column2: PAPABEAR THIS IS ALPHA BLACK. THE INTERSECTIONS ARE CLEARED. OVER.
PAPABEAR THIS IS ALPHA BLACK. WE GOT THE HILL. I REPEAT WE GOT THE HILL. OVER.
PAPABEAR THIS IS CHARLIE BLACK. LARUNS HAVE BEEN CAPTURED I REPEAT LARUNS HAVE BEEN CAPTURED. ALL RUSSIANS ARE DEAD. OVER.
GOOD JOB ALPHA BLACK. PROCEED TO THE HILL. PAPABEAR OUT.
COPY CHARLIE BLACK. WE AKNOWLEDGE YOU GOT LARUNS UNDER CONTROL. OVER.
